{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"应用层协议协商","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/ALPN","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>应用层协议协商</strong>（<strong>Application-Layer Protocol Negotiation</strong>，简称<strong>ALPN</strong>）是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/TLS\">TLS</a> 的一个扩展，故而应用层协议在协商加密协议的过程中，避免了额外的往返通讯开销。</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>协议</th>\n      <th>标识符字节序列</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP\">HTTP</a>/1.1</td>\n      <td><code>0x68 0x74 0x74 0x70 0x2F 0x31 0x2E 0x31</code> (\"http/1.1\")</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP_2\">HTTP/2</a></td>\n      <td><code>0x68 0x32</code> (\"h2\")</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>HTTP/2 over cleartext <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/TCP\">TCP</a></td>\n      <td><code>0x68 0x32 0x63</code> (\"h2c\")</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Notes</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc7301\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 7301</a></td>\n      <td>IETF RFC</td>\n      <td>初始化定义</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.iana.org/assignments/tls-extensiontype-values/tls-extensiontype-values.xhtml#alpn-protocol-ids\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">IANA registered ALPN identifiers</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"应用层协议协商（Application-Layer Protocol Negotiation，简称ALPN）是 TLS 的一个扩展，故而应用层协议在协商加密协议的过程中，避免了额外的往返通讯开销。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ALPN","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ALPN","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ALPN","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/alpn","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/alpn/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/ALPN","title":"应用层协议协商"}],"pageTitle":"应用层协议协商 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}